{"name":"开源库","postlist":[{"title":"Dagger2","slug":"Dagger2","date":"2018-03-06T06:00:43.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:51:09.975Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Dagger2.json","excerpt":"Dagger2 是 Dagger 的升级版，是一个依赖注入框架。Dagger2 与其他依赖注入框架不同，它是通过 apt 插件在编译阶段生成相应的注入代码。依赖注入是面向对象编程的一种设计模式，其目的是为了降低程序耦合，这个耦合就是类之间的依赖引起的。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2018/03/06/Dagger2/Dagger2/image-201804031417535.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Data Binding 的双向绑定","slug":"Data Binding 的双向绑定","date":"2018-01-05T02:15:58.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:51:36.614Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Data Binding 的双向绑定.json","excerpt":" DataBinding 支持双向绑定，能大大减少绑定 app 逻辑与 layout 文件的“胶水代码”。双向绑定，指的是将数据与界面绑定起来，当数据发生变化时会体现在界面上，反过来界面内容变化也会同步更新到数据上，使用 DataBinding 能轻松实现 MVVM 模式。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"EventBus","slug":"EventBus","date":"2017-12-27T05:52:33.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:49:13.266Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/EventBus.json","excerpt":"EventBus 基于观察者模式的 Android 事件分发总线。它使得 事件发送 和 事件接收 很好地解耦。另外使得 Android 组件之间的通信变得简单，代码变得整洁。","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"OkHttp","slug":"OkHttp","date":"2017-12-08T05:34:07.000Z","updated":"2018-04-07T09:39:16.666Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/OkHttp.json","excerpt":"OkHttp 是一个高效的 HTTP 库:支持 SPDY ，共享同一个 Socke t来处理同一个服务器的所有请求如果 SPDY 不可用，则通过连接池来减少请求延时无缝的支持 GZIP 来减少数据流量缓存响应数据来减少重复的网络请求","keywords":null,"cover":"/2017/12/08/OkHttp/OkHttp/image-201804020012074.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Glide","slug":"Glide","date":"2017-11-30T05:24:21.000Z","updated":"2018-04-05T06:47:40.800Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Glide.json","excerpt":"Glide 是 Google 推荐的一套快速高效的图片加载框架，功能强大且使用方便。它在使用上大致分为 with、load、into 三个步骤，接下来将分别围绕这三个方法来解析。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2017/11/30/Glide/Glide/image-201804020004200.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]},{"title":"Retrofit","slug":"Retrofit","date":"2018-01-16T05:45:52.000Z","updated":"2018-04-08T06:50:44.887Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Retrofit.json","excerpt":"Retrofit 是一个 RESTful 的 HTTP 网络请求框架的封装。网络请求的工作本质上是 OkHttp 完成，而 Retrofit 仅负责网络请求接口的封装。","keywords":null,"cover":"/2018/01/16/Retrofit/Retrofit/944365-72f373fbbb960b69.png","content":null,"raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"开源库","path":"api/categories/开源库.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Android","path":"api/tags/Android.json"},{"name":"library","path":"api/tags/library.json"}]}]}